data.value: THE DOC MOUHAMMED HASSAN ALI ONE OF THE FAMOUS DOCTROS AT THE COUNTRY WAS GRADUADTED FROM TISHREEN COLLAEGE WITH MASTER DEGREE IN THE MEDICEN AT THE DIGESTIVE DEPARTMENT DOCTOR MOUHAMMED WAS FAMOUS ABOUT HIS TREAMENT WITH THE PEOPLE AND HIS DEDICATION AT HIS JOB ..DCOTOR ALI STUDIED THE MASTER AT CAMEPREDGE COLLAEGE AND GRADUAETED FORM IT WITH DESTINCTION MARK FOR HIS CREATION AND PROFISHENALITY IN HIS FIELD DOCTOR MOUHAMMED WORKED AS THE COMMANDER OF THE SENDICITY AT THE MEDICEN IN SYRIA AND DCOTOR AT DAMUSCUS COLLEGE THEN THE DOCTOR WAS ELECTIED TO BE AMBASSDOR OF THE MEDICEN IN CANADA HE GOT THE PATENINT FOR HIS DESCOVRIES AT THE MEDICEN ...IN 2009 WAS REATED AS ONE OF THE MOST TAELENTED AND MOST SKILLED DOC IN SYRIA ..DOC MOUHAMMED WAS AND STILL THE FATHER OF THE POOR PEOPLE AT HIS JOB..AND FROM OUR HEARTS WE WISH THE DOC MOUHAMMED THE BEST WISHS AT HIS WORK AND HAVIN THE GOOD TIME WITH IT
